# Installed agent skills (skills.sh)
# Real skill content lives in .agents/skills/ and is committed; the .claude/skills/*
# entries are machine-local junctions recreated via `npx skills install`. Keep our
# own geo-seo-expert skill, which is real (not a junction).
/.claude/skills/*
!/.claude/skills/geo-seo-expert/
